## 📦 How to Start Using ScholarAI

1.  **Set your API Key**:
    Open the file [.env](file:///c:/Research%20asistant/Research-asistant/.env) and replace the placeholder with your Anthropic API Key:
    `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_sk_ant_key_here`

2.  **Launch the Server**:
    Right-click [start.ps1](file:///c:/Research%20asistant/Research-asistant/start.ps1) and select **"Run with PowerShell"**.

3.  **Access the Platform**:
    Your browser will open automatically. Navigate to **http://localhost:4000** if it doesn't.

4.  **Start Researching**:
    Enter your name and you're in!
